
# SQL Commands
===============


- How to List All the Databases
- show databases;



- How to Create Database
- create database retail_db;


- How to Connect to a Database
- use retail_db;


- How to Create a Table
- create table table_name & provide the data-types;


- How to Insert Records into a Table
- Insert into customers VALUES and provide the information; 


- How to View Records in a Table
- Select * from customers;


- How to List All the tables inside a Database
- show tables;


- How to Drop a Table
- drop table table_name;


- How to Drop a Database
- drop database db_name;


- How to Know Which Database we are connected to
- select database();




